OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will quickly
OL,6,Fclear south early on, followed by a
OL,7,Ffew isolated showers through the
OL,8,Fmorning. A fine and settled day
OL,9,Fthereafter with plenty of sunshine.
OL,10,FFeeling cool in brisk northerly winds,
OL,11,Fparticularly along coastal areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear overnight skies will
OL,14,Fallow temperatures to fall away
OL,15,Fquickly, with a rural frost forming.
OL,16,FCloud will increase from the north
OL,17,Faround dawn. Winds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
