OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA band of cloud and patchy
OL,6,Flight rain will clear south by the
OL,7,Fearly afternoon. Sunny intervals to
OL,8,Ffollow, with the odd isolated blustery
OL,9,Fshower. Winds strengthening through
OL,10,Fthe day.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FFrequent blustery showers on Wednesday
OL,14,Fand Thursday, occasionally heavy with
OL,15,Fa risk of thunder. Friday dry and
OL,16,Fmostly cloudy, with some bright or
OL,17,Fsunny spells. Feeling rather cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
